Interface OrganizationSearchCriteria

  • All Superinterfaces:
    gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, Versionable
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface OrganizationSearchCriteria
extends Versionable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    Defines a organization search criteria. The OrganizationSearchCriteria entity exists only for the purposes of a search. It is not stored in the database.
